      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.Dysu4F8licjEb2FY]{Vanguard Discipline}</p>\n<p>You can manipulate the natural entropy surrounding creatures to alter how magic affects them. As a reaction when a creature with spell resistance within 30 feet is targeted by a spell, you can spend 1 Entropy Point to unravel their magical defenses. Reduce the target’s spell resistance by 4 until the end of your next turn (Will negates). Each time a spell successfully overcomes the target’s spell resistance during this time, the amount by which this effect reduces the spell resistance increases by 1. Once you’ve targeted a creature with shred magic, you can’t target that creature with this ability again for 24 hours.</p>"
